  <section condition="TITLE=System Features: License Definition;PERM=lic_access;ACCESS=SY_LIC"
           id="LID" role="TOPIC">
    <title>Overview</title>

    <para role="TEXT">As an administrator at a bank,you can add license
    definitions, which will be used by your client users in the menu
    <emphasis>Trade Services &gt; License</emphasis>. It will allow your
    customers to select a type of license defined to link it to transactions
    and allocate the amount to transactions for creation of license against
    the attributes thus defined.</para>
  </section>

  <section role="ITEM">
    <title>License Definition - Navigation</title>

    <para role="TEXT">To navigate to the <emphasis role="bold">License
    Definition</emphasis> function, from the toolbar, select <emphasis>System
    Features</emphasis> from the home page, then select <emphasis>License
    Definition</emphasis> from the left navigation menu.</para>
  </section>

  <section role="ITEM">
    <title>License Definition - List of Licenses Associated to
    Customers</title>

    <para role="TEXT">This option is used by the Bank Administrator to
    maintain License Definition details for customers. When you select this
    option, you are presented with a list of all the existing License
    Definitions at your bank. You can search the list by entering search
    criteria in the <guilabel moreinfo="none">Name</guilabel> and
    <guilabel>Type</guilabel> fields at the top of the page.</para>

    <para role="TEXT">The list of existing License Definitions has the
    following columns:</para>

    <informaltable role="TEXT">
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="2.0*"/>

        <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="8.0*"/>

        <thead>
          <row>
            <entry valign="top"><para>Field</para></entry>

            <entry valign="top"><para>Description</para></entry>
          </row>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry valign="top"><para> <guilabel
            moreinfo="none">Name</guilabel> </para></entry>

            <entry valign="top"><para>Name of the license
            definition.</para></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry valign="top"><para> <guilabel
            moreinfo="none">Type</guilabel> </para></entry>

            <entry valign="top"><para>Type of License. The options are: Import
            License, Export License and FX License.</para></entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry valign="top"><para> <guilabel moreinfo="none">Associated
            Customers</guilabel> </para></entry>

            <entry valign="top"><para>Customers linked to the license
            definition.</para></entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
