    <para role="TEXT">You can modify a License Definition by clicking the
    <guiicon moreinfo="none">Edit</guiicon> <inlinemediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_edit.gif" role="ICON_EDIT"
                     width="4mm"/>
        </imageobject>
      </inlinemediaobject> icon in the right-hand column, or delete it by
    clicking the <guibutton moreinfo="none">Delete</guibutton>
    <inlinemediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_trash.gif" role="ICON_TRASH"
                     width="4mm"/>
        </imageobject>
      </inlinemediaobject> icon. Click the <guibutton moreinfo="none">Add a
    New License Definition</guibutton> button at the bottom of the list to add
    a License Definition. <guiicon moreinfo="none">Edit</guiicon> and
    <guibutton moreinfo="none">Add</guibutton> display the same form, but in
    the case of <guibutton moreinfo="none">Edit</guibutton> it is preset with
    the details of an existing License Definition. After entering the details,
    click <emphasis role="bold">Save</emphasis> at the bottom of the
    form.</para>

